messages.message:
Everyone - We have decided to push back the internal launch of AI hub by two weeks to *May 15th.* We are going to use the time to polish existing user journeys, and finish work on remaining user journeys (e.g. usage based billing, loginless experience with rate limits).

I know that all of you are eagerly awaiting to test out the new experience, and share your feedback. Thanks for your patience, give us a bit more time to craft a great experience we all can be proud of.

Please donâ€™t try out the aihub.dev (http://aihub.dev) environment meanwhile. It is going to have frequent deployments over the next two weeks, and not meant for user testing and feedback. We will release the internal preview on a separate staging environment. You can continue using the AI Labs GTM sandbox for testing and demos.

If there are any questions, let us know.

cc: @Ashish @Kerry @shaunak
